mediately appreciated when I slept under this bedding. \u0026#39;Soft material on the reverse, so no waffle pillow marks!\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter all, waffles may be the bedding choice of the moment, but they should still stay where they belong: on the bed and not imprinted onto your face in the morning!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
